Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:56.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:02:00.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Did I just see the ghost of a\NRoad Racer who died here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}His first counter-steer was a motion to\Nget the right angle for the left curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:13.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It was the perfect drift of a driver who\Nknows everything about Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:23.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, did you see that Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:27.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My pride is torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:33.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My FD, with its mountain setup, was beaten\Nby a 10 year old Eight-Six junker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What the hell is that Eight-Six?
