Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.24,0:02:45.51,TITLE,,0150,0000,0395,,{\fad(719,679)\pos(59,169)\blur1.5}ACT.2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi!  Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are you gonna sleep?\NGet up!  You've got a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Itsuki, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, hurry and\Npick up the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:35.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was about time\Nto restore our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Restore, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:41.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But we weren't in a fight or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were talking about\Ncars at school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you drive, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just got a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:55.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go driving somewhere\Nduring summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:59.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You drive and I'll fix lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I only have a dorky one for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind. It at least has a\Ncassette deck, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what the car is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun.\NI'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we drive a long way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NThe ocean would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim together, since it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt, it's the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I bet the fastest on Akina is\Nthe tofu shop's Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:00.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is this... the fastest machine\Non the downhill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It looks like it's an\Nordinary Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:08.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}An early Apex model,\Nexcept for the fog lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:13.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}A car like this can't be faster\Nthan the latest machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must be wrong\Nwith me, searching for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nin front of my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:42.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I had something to do, and...\NI was just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:47.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Takumi, you really don't\Nknow anything about cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you didn't know about\Nthe Eight-Six yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:57.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the car at your house\Nis an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:02.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.\NIt's not an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It says Trueno on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, a Trueno is an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:14.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Levins and Truenos with the chassis\Ntype AE86 are called Eight-Six.{Corolla SR5 in the U.S.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,An Eight-Six at Takumi's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:22.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you keep it a secret?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped,\Nbecause I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a Trueno, why\Ndon't you say Trueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:38.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Eight-Six."\NOrdinary people don't call them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I have\Nsomething to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you borrow the Eight-Six\Nnext Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:48.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:55.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go watch the gathering\Nof the Speedstars and Redsuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:07:00.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that incident yesterday,\NI'm really into the Road Racer world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:05.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to see how the Takahashi\Nbrothers, the fastest on Akagi, drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really my friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:18.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you to drive your\NEight-Six on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Welcome!{\r}\NWelcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Installing brand new tires?\NYou've really spoiled yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to cut my time by\Ninstalling high grip tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also change the brake pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brakes are important on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to run, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:58.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tackle the downhill of Akina like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:03.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.\NOne mistake'll kill you on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but I have to push it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the locals' pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:37.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That Eight-Six didn't\Nshow up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He isn't a Road Racer\Nfrom this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:44.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No.  He knew everything\Nabout Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I want to see it again,\Nand get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...or I won't be able\Nto calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Come out, ghost of Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't care about the Speedstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm here to face you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:05.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like the drift king,\NTsuchiya Keiichi!  I can't sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be controlling it\Nusing only acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:15.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, I wish we could soon\Nperform a drift like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:15.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:19.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that drift!\NIt's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You only say "yeah, yeah!"\NDo you really know what drift is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know what drift is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, explain what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the curve...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say curve, it sounds so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers call them corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:46.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:51.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you steer like this to let the front tires go\Noutward so the car won't face the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If the front tires go outward,\Nyou're experiencing understeering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows your poor skill,\Nand it's totally uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You let the rear go\Noutward when you drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strange.\NYou're incredible, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}You're the one who\Ndoesn't know, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:21.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}When the car is drifting, it's supposed\Nto be understeered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:26.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It was the advanced answer of those who\Nhave mastered the four-wheel drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a customer.\NLet's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,O...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:49.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi Keisuke's FD?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,High octane, fill it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really devoted, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:09.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd seen that S13.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the Speedstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ghost on Mt. Akina, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost of an extremely fast Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:39.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, does he want\Nto fly or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:42.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't joke around with me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking about\Nthe ghost part...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's about a black and\Nwhite panda Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:53.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The exterior looks like a normal Eight-Six,\Nbut it's an incredible monster inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A local guy should know about\Nsuch an incredible car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:05.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's your secret weapon for Saturday,\NI'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the driver of the Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:11.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I won't let the same\Nguy defeat me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:16.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost because I wasn't familiar with\Nthe course and got careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:24.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi Keisuke lost...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:28.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I didn't know any\NEight-Six could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:38.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But the one at Takumi's house\Nis also a panda Trueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is what the manager said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The fastest on the downhill\Nis still that Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that does it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more than usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just don't spill it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look as sleepy as usual, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but my face\Nis like this naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:42.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget your Eight-Six\Non next Saturday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.  You're so persistent, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:49.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be persistent or I can't\Nclear my doubts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Saturday would come early!\NI'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, since we hope\Nto be Road Racers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...we want to be called the fastest\Non Akina some day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's probably impossible,\Neven if you try...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:12.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you don't have a bit of talent, being\Nscared in the rear seat of Iketani's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a bit scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:19.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I could look at the sharp corners,\Nclenching my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani must have thought that there\Nwould be no hope for Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:26.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:32.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:40.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're jealous of\Nmy talent, you're too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:40.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Say what?\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:46.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rumiko told my boyfriend\Nabout it.  He's so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,N...no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:55.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crime to make their skirts so\Nshort without thinking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The school should regulate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,M...Mogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have something to talk to you about.\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:15.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what the hell?!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:40.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:46.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...bought a new bathing suit!\NIt's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:54.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was so excited and I wanted\Nto tell somebody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see it soon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:06.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see it as much as you\Nwant when we go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...just...look...forward...to...it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this Sunday?\NAre you free?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll do.\NPromise me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't break promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:24.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like a person who breaks\Npromises or smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, it's so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:54.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The dull corners now appear to be\Nthe scary and tight ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:59.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Those familiar corners challenge\Nme so differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even if I push myself to the limit,\NI can't shorten the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I thought if I depressed the accelerator\Nmore, I could cut the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:33.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:36.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is this the best my technique can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:40.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There's no way I can compete with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!  Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you.\NWait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:07.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is he the Eight-Six driver who's\Nthe fastest on Akina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is he the Road Racer who can\Nbeat Takahashi Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a fried tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:17.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:24.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:28.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm with a team called\Nthe Akina Speedstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:37.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I... heard a strange rumor that the\Nfastest on Mt. Akina's downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...is an old guy from a tofu shop,\Nwho drives an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:44.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who said that,\Nbut it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't pretend\Nnot to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I searched\Nthe entire city...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't be able to find another tofu\Nshop man who drives an Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.  140 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,O...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm in a complicated situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trouble me.\NI'm working now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:11.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look bored!\NNo one else is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude, saying something directly\Nthat should've been held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'm desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:24.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, a team called the Akagi Redsuns\Nchallenged us to a time attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:32.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some highly skilled guys with the\NRedsuns, and we're no match for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:36.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be defeated\Nas a local driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara, I want you to teach me\Nhow to tackle Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be satisfied, even if it shortens\Nthe time by a tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:21:02.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, but driving technique is\Nnot something you can obtain in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to think over and over how you\Ncan make the car run as you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:08.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and keep on driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:13.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was actively driving,\NI tackled Akina even in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:19.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Technique isn't something to be taught,\Nyou must acquire it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I can't be of help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara, I'll visit you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Think it over and over\Nand keep on driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm trying, but I can't cut my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:04.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Dammit. I can't figure it out,\Nno matter how hard I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't dodge him!\NPlease, escape to the inside!
